0 - You need at least PHP 5.4
1 - Get Composer : https://getcomposer.org/doc/00-intro.md#globally
2 - Open a terminal in this directory and tape the command: composer update
3 - (optional) Generate the documentation of the source code with bin/generate-doc
4 - (optional) Generate the unit test code coverage documentation with bin/phpunit-coverage
5 - (optional) Execute the unit tests with bin/phpunit-test